properties.name: Haroldston Farmhouse is a large detached self-catering holiday cottage
properties.description: Posted by Pembs  Haroldston Farmhouse is a large detached self-catering holiday cottage, in beautiful open countryside, just outside the market town of Haverfordwest and is ideally placed to explore the whole of this stunning county of Pembrokeshire. The house is fully equipped and can comfortably accommodate 12 adults, so is ideal for a large family holiday or club outing. The games room has a proper bar pool table. Whilst the house is conveniently placed within easy reach of shops, pubs and restaurants it remains tranquil at the end of it\'s own 300 yard long drive. The beach is only 15 minutes away.

properties.name: Tenby Museum & Art Gallery Tenby Pembrokeshire
properties.description: Posted by Pembs   One of the oldest surviving independent museums in the United Kingdom, Tenby Museum and Art Gallery is a non-profit making charitable trust, run almost exclusively by volunteers. The museum works closely with national and regional museums throughout Wales and elsewhere. Tenby Museum has gained many national and regional awards and has earned the reputation of being one of the best museums of its kind in the country.
